**BTC Mart** features free online classified advertisements for goods and services where the seller accepts bitcoins. It supports Russian and English.

The site was announced January 16, 2011 (1.1)

This is the first site that to specifically feature online classifieds for Bitcoin-related [[eCommerce|tags/ECommerce]] though classified ads on Craigslist have been seen where the payment terms either allowed or required payment with bitcoins (1.2)

